A test suite with tests for SDWAN SINGLE CPE Solution. Testplan Goals:- 1. CHECK WAN INTERFACES STATUS. 2. CHECK BGP NEIGHBOR STATUS. 3. CHECK LAN ROUTE. 4. Ping Test. 5. IPERF Test.
